{"tid":845370,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"教練的雞雞很大、很黑、很長，「幫教練舒服」　前跆拳國手猥褻男童遭判刑","createTime":"2018-10-02T14:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T04:31:33.000Z","uid":1426,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc61c87cdb4dc85e400e2ad3e19b6edf0537756","tid":845370,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T14:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.ibaby.org.tw/Upload/2015/11/20151124235754596.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibaby.org.tw%2FUpload%2F2015%2F11%2F20151124235754596.png&h=ae58c84e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前跆拳國手蘇俊豪涉猥褻男童，還對男童說：「我已幫你舒服，你也幫教練舒服。」示意圖<br />\n<br />\n曾當選跆拳國手的28歲男子蘇俊豪，前年9月在新北市一間道館擔任跆拳教練期間，涉嫌利用帶一名當時5歲的男學員上廁所的機會，猥褻男童下體並說：「我已幫你舒服，你也幫教練舒服。」要男童摸他下體。新北地院今依對未滿14歲猥褻罪判蘇男3年半徒刑。<br />\n <br />\n蘇男是台灣師範大學運動競技學系碩士，曾入選國家代表隊並獲世界青少年跆拳道錦標賽銀牌、英國跆拳道公開賽「最佳美技獎」，與奧運跆拳道國手黃志雄、宋玉麒為同門師兄弟。<br />\n <br />\n判決指出，2013年9月10日蘇男擔任新北市某跆拳道館的指導教練期間，上課前帶僅學習跆拳1個多月的5歲男童入廁，等男童上完廁所，蘇男竟要他站在馬桶上，猥褻男童下體並說「我已幫你舒服，你也幫教練舒服」，要男童也摸他下體。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">男童返家告訴媽媽「教練的雞雞很大、很黑、很長」，媽媽追問得知兒子遭猥褻怒提告。<br />\n</span><br />\n蘇男辯稱當天帶男童上廁所，不小心碰到，所謂「舒服」是指上完廁所的感覺，意思是問男童上完廁所有沒有舒服，而他也要上廁所舒服一下。<br />\n <br />\n不過，新北地院根據男童描述及台大醫院對男童鑑定結果，認定男童陳述為真，且男童早就會自己上廁所，而監視畫面顯示男童、蘇男進廁所到離開，時間長達6分鐘，就算2人輪流上廁所也不用這麼久，因此認定蘇男犯行明確，今判他3年半徒刑。仍可上訴。（孫友廉／新北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ibaby.org.tw/Upload/2015/11/20151125000116752.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibaby.org.tw%2FUpload%2F2015%2F11%2F20151125000116752.png&h=a68452ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前跆拳國手蘇俊豪涉猥褻男童遭判刑。翻攝照片"},{"pid":"1f6248a37b9301c1626121e96f4bb24239c569c4","tid":845370,"uid":48942,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"都幾樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6094ab7743be2f517933e35da8489e3981bde654","tid":845370,"uid":173208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:00:01.000Z","msg":"約炮?"},{"pid":"be6cbcb7457acb612428684f8b772e65f6ba8ae5","tid":845370,"uid":95264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:00:51.000Z","msg":"新北市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed7b0a0683460033ada4c4ab337eefdb5dc401f","tid":845370,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:02:49.000Z","msg":"最美的風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d244d480d1fe642dd4e6cdcf18290006424c3c","tid":845370,"uid":57232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"睇個樣就知變態佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9c3a595e5d2e0b0018303d7fbbeaf7832a6d87","tid":845370,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:34:09.000Z","msg":"很大 很黑 很長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd 描述好寫實<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19fe55c23fac267609b097287d5cacb5b24fd77","tid":845370,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44e90a68e026e09510647ad660bd0c1a5ae44084","tid":845370,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:38:52.000Z","msg":"醬爆"},{"pid":"95dbaacc8305483d9f445b0041436cadf71f1815","tid":845370,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T16:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f518fc9acf63b4ddba543e49b96348cca8de8fe","tid":845370,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:30:08.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"1a3d8a2715fd31e195e782d7ebbe4fb